ocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/558447412","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545616568,"updated_time":1545616568,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e远离哥猜，享受生活。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e哥猜吸引了无数民科，因为看似问题简单，事实上是触不可及的，不懂高等数学，只会初等数论的，是几乎不可能证出来，(为了说话严谨，我加了几乎，事实上是根本不可能)，还是脚踏实地的认真学习吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你喜欢数学，最后高考进大学后可以选择数学专业，如果你对数论感兴趣，研究生你可以选择基础数学专业数论方向，如果进去深造，博士你可以做解析数论或者代数数论。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e另外，也不是非要去清华北大才能学习，其他学校你照样可以学数学。学校牛不牛逼，跟你关系不大，你自己不努力读书，去再好的学校也没用，除了可以获得一些虚无的虚荣。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":558420984,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"722d37955f46e361c3dcdcf12c4f00c6","url_token":"xu-ce-2-66","name":"赤城霞","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-85259bcfa466da48d938f41f597d4af0_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-85259bcfa466da48d938f41f597d4af0_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/722d37955f46e361c3dcdcf12c4f00c6","user_type":"people","headline":"生物狗","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/558420984","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545614303,"updated_time":1545970308,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e都当皇帝了还想着顿顿吃烧饼吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e补充，所有试图鼓励题主的答主，非蠢既坏。这世界也许会存在比欧拉伽罗华拉马努金还聪明的非人天才，但是那种天才绝不会问出，能不能保研清华这种蠢话。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":558105308,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/558105308","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545564956,"updated_time":1545564956,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e当然能了。而且你要能证明了这个，估计也就看不上清北了吧...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ep.s. 如果你只是把这个当一个命题问，那我告诉你可以，但容我多说一句，如果你想以此上清北，送你四个大字：想都别想。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562664352,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562664352","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546132576,"updated_time":1546132576,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这个世界是怎么了？怎么这么多冷嘲热讽的人。证明了又怎么样，没证明又怎么样。高中又怎么样不是高中又怎么样，别人还不能有个梦想吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  万一真的是个天才呢，另辟蹊径，找到了一天新路。可是就是犹豫你们种种嘲讽，变得怀疑自己，不敢正视他，社会的莫大悲哀。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  好高骛远，那也是别人的事，谁年轻还没摔过一个跟头啊。装了南墙才知道回头，不涉深山，又哪知天地之大。这才叫做成长啊，总比你们一个个认命了的，向命运低头了的人好吧，完全就是一百步笑零步，逃跑的多的逃兵在嘲笑还没有跑的，\"傻子，你怎么打得过敌人，你能一打一千一个吗？\"。逃兵！嘲笑着一个想要拼搏到最后的人，还想要鼓动别人和他一起逃跑。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  社会的悲哀。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561334595,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"fd4155c2ae5473dfc0e5322d9b5ecf7f","url_token":"superjun-bao","name":"魏内子","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2235054a48ada6dbd450a74dbd9192bc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2235054a48ada6dbd450a74dbd9192bc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/fd4155c2ae5473dfc0e5322d9b5ecf7f","user_type":"people","headline":"仍未忘跟你相约假如没有死","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561334595","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545959927,"updated_time":1545959927,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e同学你好，我不太懂数学，但是看到你的故事却想对你说句加油！希望你不管遇到什么挫折，都能坚持自己热爱的事情，遇到喜欢的事情不容易。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560697558,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"ab4e528d71008bdecbe82bfa12eb2a01","url_token":"song-ze-kun-86","name":"花开不败","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6217bc9e7a7db77a0322d0b60fc8e39d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6217bc9e7a7db77a0322d0b60fc8e39d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/ab4e528d71008bdecbe82bfa12eb2a01","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560697558","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545880186,"updated_time":1545880207,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不能，因为高等学府不要自不量力的白痴\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560588952,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"d2ed40a5145493b1ca8571e2a935797c","url_token":"wei-ma-gong-he-guo","name":"魏玛共和国","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/d2ed40a5145493b1ca8571e2a935797c","user_type":"people","headline":"审批官","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560588952","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545871956,"updated_time":1545871956,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"首先确保读题准确，年轻人很容易看错题目的。","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560577370,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"e720d18db2500d815ef911302d3fc03e","url_token":"peng-rong-58","name":"大大的荣德龙","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ba010fe9bec64f94db94ef23cda51a2d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ba010fe9bec64f94db94ef23cda51a2d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/e720d18db2500d815ef911302d3fc03e","user_type":"people","headline":"未来石油人，在校大学生","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560577370","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545870705,"updated_time":1545873438,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e保送这个得问学校呀~\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我主要想说想做就做，做自己喜欢的事很好\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e年轻人能在自己喜欢的路上走着，很棒\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但要劳逸结合，注意身心健康\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看了部分回答与评论，有嘲讽有鼓励\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e网络就是这个样子，声音多种\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后，偏科是不好滴，有时间可以注意其他科目\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560547256,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560547256","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545862058,"updated_time":1545862058,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e其实我和你同样作为一名只有一科比较突出的人，我非常的理解你，但是可惜的是我并没有你那么精通，成绩也只是在班级里比较高而已。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还有想说一句，各大网友也不要再冷嘲热讽了，这对于一个高中生的伤害也是很大的，说者无意听者伤心。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e好了回归正题，我支持你发表，如果这是对的那么这在学术界绝对是一个尤为惊人的发现，然后你名利双收，如果有一点点问题，那么这也会为后人提供一个思路啥啥的，也不乏是一个好的结果。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实这个世界不缺乏人才，不过很多多没有机会崭露头角，高考的制服确实不是擅长一颗就可以上一个好学校的，这也是我一直在苦恼的事，不要说清华北大，911285的门槛对我来说都有点高，同学说我你××都能学好为什么别的了不行。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实热情这种东西真的很难被分走的不是吗。所以我理解你，也支持你。无论是否发表，是对是错，至少我站在你这边。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以及，，，，，数学大佬给抱大腿吗233／挂掉！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以上！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e祝好运。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560508101,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"abc1673884320d878033bfa27906004e","url_token":"feng-yuan-57-21","name":"风源","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-535387b84c2d1a04a712a878f3188718_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-535387b84c2d1a04a712a878f3188718_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/abc1673884320d878033bfa27906004e","user_type":"people","headline":"未来程序员","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560508101","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545844642,"updated_time":1545844642,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e您好\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我是一个算是蛮垃圾的本科生吧，我没资格评论什么哥猜证明的balabala，但看见知乎上有部分人发表的言论有些偏激，我不禁想表达一下我的见解\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1.如果你真的成功证明了哥猜而且没有任何问题了话，那么你肯定是很有天赋并且很努力的人，你的未来一片光明，请保持下去。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2.如果你花了很长时间付出了很大努力证明出来了哥猜但是你的猜想被人指出问题了话，我也同样相信你是一位十分有才华的人，我在高中认识个和你一样爱钻研学术攻克难题的人，他现在也十分优秀，所以请保持这样的势头，加油!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3.如果你证明出来了哥猜却存在很严重的问题而自己没有发现了话，希望你能在今后的学习生涯中严谨行事，这不是敢于发表言论而是莽撞，这样无异于是\"民科\"证法，一定确保自己在搞清所有概念论述的情况下去谈证明，科学要讲严谨。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e4.如果你没证出来只是耍我们了话，那么一点都不好笑= =\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560415567,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c73839a2724195071993bd02c47f9b18","url_token":"wu-wang-2-92","name":"无妄","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-5aeeab07e1c1e4a86369c7399b9c1ab9_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-5aeeab07e1c1e4a86369c7399b9c1ab9_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c73839a2724195071993bd02c47f9b18","user_type":"people","headline":"生如夏花 ","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560415567","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-cce8b91dd9d2122f54524f510f33da1a_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545835957,"updated_time":1545836753,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e对于一个高中生来说，现阶段的目标就是考到一个好大学。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看到一圈评论多半认为题主的证明是错的，看轻了哥猜，还有嘲讽的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也不知道题主看到回复的心情如何。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果题主能够证明成功非常开心了！如果错误也不要太过沮丧，你才高中，还非常年轻，只要是自己的思考也还是很有意义的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有梦没有错，但要付之行动。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e作为高中生还是好好学习努力考上好的大学，这样有更多的时间精力做你热爱的东西，好好加油！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e290aa077a2d8503ab7211613ef38d35_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"684\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6a2600ddcfe4218155cdf4c4a61d0ff9_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e290aa077a2d8503ab7211613ef38d35_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='720'%20height='684'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"684\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6a2600ddcfe4218155cdf4c4a61d0ff9_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e290aa077a2d8503ab7211613ef38d35_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e290aa077a2d8503ab7211613ef38d35_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560330240,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"15668d3d33c1fd17a3af6f2c5f79d778","url_token":"li-ling-xia-98","name":"黎泠夏","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/15668d3d33c1fd17a3af6f2c5f79d778","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560330240","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545829758,"updated_time":1545837271,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不管怎么样总归比我厉害orz 就算是错误的也比我厉害啊……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e本来就没啥大事评论都那么……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e人家只是提出了自己的想法 如果错了等他发了大佬们再来指出就好了啊\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而且就算是错误的证明，但也可能是独一无二的想法啊？分享一下不行吗 总之都没必要在评论里嘲讽吧\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=1680\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=1640\u0026sort_by=default","totals":1823}}
